SQLLoaderMapping.name: Volume to biomass parameters
SQLLoaderMapping.fetch_sql:
SELECT
                A, B, a_nonmerch, b_nonmerch, k_nonmerch, cap_nonmerch, a_sap, b_sap,
                k_sap, cap_sap, a1, a2, a3, b1, b2, b3, c1, c2, c3, min_volume, max_volume,
                low_stemwood_prop, high_stemwood_prop, low_stembark_prop, high_stembark_prop,
                low_branches_prop, high_branches_prop, low_foliage_prop, high_foliage_prop
            FROM tblBioTotalStemwoodSpeciesTypeDefault
            UNION
            SELECT
                A, B, a_nonmerch, b_nonmerch, k_nonmerch, cap_nonmerch, a_sap, b_sap,
                k_sap, cap_sap, a1, a2, a3, b1, b2, b3, c1, c2, c3, min_volume, max_volume,
                low_stemwood_prop, high_stemwood_prop, low_stembark_prop, high_stembark_prop,
                low_branches_prop, high_branches_prop, low_foliage_prop, high_foliage_prop
            FROM tblBioTotalStemwoodGenusDefault
            UNION
            SELECT A, B, a_nonmerch, b_nonmerch, k_nonmerch, cap_nonmerch, a_sap, b_sap,
                k_sap, cap_sap, a1, a2, a3, b1, b2, b3, c1, c2, c3, min_volume, max_volume,
                low_stemwood_prop, high_stemwood_prop, low_stembark_prop, high_stembark_prop,
                low_branches_prop, high_branches_prop, low_foliage_prop, high_foliage_prop
            FROM tblBioTotalStemwoodForestTypeDefault
